bridge_deposit_instructions_full: Once your transaction has confirmed on Ethereum, it takes roughly 7-8 minutes for your balance to reflect on Polygon. Your balance will update automatically.
bridge_withdraw_instructions_full: Withdrawing from Polygon takes approximately 2-3 hours, sometimes longer. After the withdrawal is complete, you still need to click 'CLAIM ON ETHEREUM' to get your tokens on Ethereum Mainnet.
